Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBInterface

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBInterface
public class JDBInterface
extends java.lang.Object
JDBInterface is used to insert/update/delete records from the SYS_INTERFACE table. This table holds the configuration for all inbound and outbound interfaces.

See Also:
JInternalFrameInterfaceAdmin, JInternalFrameInterfaceProperties, JDBInterfaceLog
